    "Projected the manipulation leg upward and identified an old high resting in the projection area as the first target.",
    "Defined entry on the CISD / order block formed by the down-close candles, with stop on the manipulation low.",
    "Tracked price reaching the old high target, consolidating, then continuing to reach the -4 standard deviation projection."
